Novile Editor
=============

Novile is an editor for Qt 5, based on Ace editor from ajax.org. It allows to extend your application with pretty source code editor, full of features.

If you ask us to describe it in 5 words, we will say: beautiful, powerful, extensible, light-weight and just awesome. Created with Qt 5, created for Qt 5 - Novile offers the biggest cross-platform power you can even think about. Enjoy it!

Useful links:
=============
http://ace.ajax.org/ - Ace Editor
https://github.com/tucnak - Author of the library
